                  </hi>. I live at 92, Gibraltar Wharf—on this evening I saw the prosecutor walking down the Bethnal Green Road—two persons Attacked him—Allen was one—the other man caught him by the throat and dashed him into the gutter; the prisoner knelt upon his chest—two policemen came up when I did.</p>
